articles.title: Google Chrome
articles.description: Chrome is a web browser developed by Google, released in 2008. Chrome is the world's most popular web browser today.

articles.title: Mozilla Firefox
articles.description: Mozilla Firefox is an open-source web browser developed by Mozilla. Firefox has been the second most popular web browser since January, 2018.

articles.title: Microsoft Edge
articles.description: Microsoft Edge is a web browser developed by Microsoft, released in 2015. Microsoft Edge replaced Internet Explorer.
